## Frontend environment template (Vite)
## Create a .env file locally with these values (do NOT commit secrets)

VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:5000

## ⛓️ Smart Contract Configuration (Required for MetaMask integration)
## Get the contract address after deploying the smart contract to Polygon Mumbai:
## 1. Run: forge create --chain=80001 src/AlumniVerification.sol:AlumniVerification --constructor-args "Institution Name"
## 2. Copy the deployed contract address and paste here
VITE_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0xYOUR_DEPLOYED_CONTRACT_ADDRESS_HERE

## Polygon Mumbai RPC URL (optional - frontend uses MetaMask provider)
VITE_RPC_URL=https://rpc-mumbai.maticvigil.com
